a comeback like this?

27:03.955 --> 27:05.165
It's one of those games

27:05.248 --> 27:07.042
where it doesn't matter
who wins or loses.

27:07.125 --> 27:08.710
Oh, yes, it does, buddy.

27:08.793 --> 27:10.253
McHale has the ball
at the foul line.

27:10.337 --> 27:11.504
He's already missed
the first of two.

27:11.588 --> 27:14.049
But the Celts only need one
to take the game here tonight.

27:14.132 --> 27:15.342
McHale sets, and it's good!

27:15.425 --> 27:16.718
Yes, yes!

