32:22.357 --> 32:24.859
{\an1}Give me a minute,
would you?

32:24.942 --> 32:26.527
{\an3}Yeah, I know, but
make it fast.

32:26.611 --> 32:28.529
It's starting
Yeah, yeah, okay.

32:28.613 --> 32:30.531
You want to step
into my office?

32:30.615 --> 32:31.282
Lead the way.

32:34.077 --> 32:36.037
Brandon, uh...

32:36.120 --> 32:39.040
{\an1}I don't know how to tell you
this exactly, but, um,

32:39.123 --> 32:42.001
{\an1}I mean, it's unusual
for me, but...

32:42.085 --> 32:43.211
{\an1}I'm going to need
a little more time.

32:43.294 --> 32:44.253
What?!

32:44.337 --> 32:46.756
I'm good for it,
really I am.

32:46.839 --> 32:47.757
{\an1}It's just, this weekend
kind of stacked up...

32:47.840 --> 32:49.384
What was all that crap
you told me at school?

32:49.467 --> 32:50.677
I can cover your action,
Brandon, no problem.

32:50.760 --> 32:52.553
I thought I could,
but it's either you,

32:52.637 --> 32:54.222
or the whole football team,
and you are a lot smaller.

32:54.305 --> 32:56.224
(laughs)

32:56.307 --> 32:57.183
{\an1}This isn't
Brandon,man.

32:57.266 --> 32:59.060
it's no big deal really.

32:59.143 --> 33:00.395
I'll pay off.

33:00.478 --> 33:01.062
{\an1}I've been in business
a long time.

33:01.145 --> 33:03.564
I don't welch.

33:03.648 --> 33:06.025
How could you take a bet
you couldn't cover, huh?

33:06.109 --> 33:07.360
You know what I
could do to you?

33:07.443 --> 33:09.404
Do you? Do you?!

33:09.487 --> 33:11.197
Brandon, calm down.

33:11.280 --> 33:12.573
Don't tell me
to calm down.

33:12.657 --> 33:13.783
{\an3}Don't you say
anything to me.

33:13.866 --> 33:15.576
{\an3}You just listen to me
for a minute, all right?

33:15.660 --> 33:16.786
(tires screeching)

33:16.869 --> 33:18.037
{\an3}You're going to
get me that money,

33:18.121 --> 33:19.580
and you're going
to get it for me

33:19.664 --> 33:20.915
{\an3}in 24 hours, you
understand me?

33:20.998 --> 33:21.582
Brandon,
what the hell are you doing?

33:21.666 --> 33:22.333
{\an3}I don't care
how you get it.

33:22.417 --> 33:23.251
I don't care who
you have to beg.

33:23.334 --> 33:24.293
{\an3}I don't care if you
have to steal it.

33:24.377 --> 33:26.421
{\an3}I want the money,
you understand?

33:26.504 --> 33:27.422
{\an3}You give me the money,
or I'm gonna break

33:27.505 --> 33:28.589
every bone in your body.

33:28.673 --> 33:30.299
{\an1}Steve, man, get this guy
off me! He's crazy!

33:30.383 --> 33:32.510
Brandon, go inside.
You better watch it.

33:32.593 --> 33:35.054
(thudding, debris clattering)

33:35.138 --> 33:36.347
(panting)

33:36.431 --> 33:39.016
